{"tid":436482,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真] 女朋友話未ready好拍拖","createTime":"2017-10-15T07:36:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-15T15:15:50.000Z","uid":136602,"like":5,"dislike":115,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"53715e39c5571c1ba216cba53ae5863ea3f26009","tid":436482,"uid":136602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T07:36:38.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我女朋友 &mdash; 叫佢做Annie啦 (假名)<br />\n佢啱啱同佢嘅Ex散咗無耐<br />\n然後我同佢由某種渠道 <br />\n由hi bye friend <br />\n做咗乜都傾嘅朋友<br />\n前後時間都只係大概半個月<br />\n就係呢半個月 比較後期嘅時候<br />\n佢就開始暗示鍾意我<br />\n咁我亦都對佢有好感<br />\n於是我就約佢出去食飯<br />\n咁就一齊咗<br />\n<br />\n咁我同Annie一齊咗之後<br />\n其實都幾sweet<br />\n詳細內容就唔多講啦<br />\n事隔2個禮拜之後<br />\nAnnie就同我講<br />\n話佢未ready好拍拖<br />\n認為我哋2個發展得太快<br />\n不過佢係鍾意我嘅 (佢自己同我講)<br />\n咁當然我都鍾意佢<br />\n<br />\n咁多位萬能嘅連登巴絲打 我應該點做好<br />\n利申: 無綠帽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62074685f020aa9986cc55a1e4f6cabeedf1aee0","tid":436482,"uid":91152,"like":121,"dislike":0,"score":121,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T07:39:34.000Z","msg":"人地騎牛搵馬<br />\n而家有旬盤咪叫你做後備 乜撚野未準備好"},{"pid":"6204319c1585a7dd615a49272a2d564e86a90e13","tid":436482,"uid":5102,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T07:40:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\">同你未ready好</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44916b96071ffffe1879bda88ca18f795dc76d33","tid":436482,"uid":139828,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T07:41:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0460166e4a3c4e7d7ecdead637df25d7b8709fa3","tid":436482,"uid":136602,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T07:43:35.000Z","msg":"屌 都話唔關綠帽事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n認真討論好無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20576e42d004e00ccd4d97142d0386dedb780af9","tid":436482,"uid":13641